screen_desc: The screenshot shows the Uber app interface. At the top, there is a search bar to enter a pickup point and a button to select the time (default set to "Now"). Below the search bar, there are two promotional banners. The first banner on the left has a green background with the text "Want better pick-ups?" and an illustration of a person looking through binoculars. The second banner on the right has a light purple background with the text "Ready? Then let’s roll. Ride with Uber" and an image of a person opening a car door. At the bottom of the screen, there is a navigation bar with icons for Home, Services, Activity, and Account. The Home icon is highlighted. The status bar at the top shows the time as 8:32 AM and various status icons for notifications, network, and battery.
